OL,3,CGuernsey's health service will be
OL,4,C'overwhelmed' unless focus changes
OL,6,FGuernsey's Director of Public Health
OL,7,Fsays the island needs to strike a
OL,8,Fbetter balance between acute care and
OL,9,Fpreventing illness to stop services
OL,10,Ffrom being overwhelmed in the next 20
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FDr Nicola Brink believes the health
OL,14,Fsystem needs a longer-term vision
OL,15,Fbehind it to create a healthier and
OL,16,Fmore productive population.
