OL,3,CGuernsey's health service will be
OL,4,C'overwhelmed' unless focus changes
OL,6,FIt follows the release of the Medical
OL,7,FOfficer of Health report which
OL,8,Fincludes findings from a recent island-
OL,9,Fwise wellbeing survey and disease
OL,10,Fmodelling.
OL,12,FDr Brink adds: "What we're saying is
OL,13,Fif we shift that focus to prevention
OL,14,Fand early intervention, we'll be able
OL,15,Fto flatten that curve of multi-
OL,16,Fmorbidity."
OL,18,FMulti-morbidity refers to when a
OL,19,Fperson has multiple chronic conditions.
