OL,3,CGuernsey's health service will be
OL,4,C'overwhelmed' unless focus changes
OL,6,FDisease modelling up to 2043 projects
OL,7,F10 out of 11 chronic diseases are set
OL,8,Fto see increases in Guernsey, with
OL,9,Fdementia cases potentially growing by
OL,10,F61% compared to 2023.
OL,12,FThe Medical Officer of Health report
OL,13,Fidentifies six goals Dr Brink would
OL,14,Flike to see reached on the island in
OL,15,Fthe next five to ten years to help
OL,16,Freduce the demand for acute care.
OL,18,FGuernsey's healthcare goals
