OL,3,CGuernsey's health service will be
OL,4,C'overwhelmed' unless focus changes
OL,6,FWhile Dr Brink believes these goals
OL,7,Fare achievable, she says they are only
OL,8,Fpossible with support, including from
OL,9,Fthe Government.
OL,11,FShe wants to see Guernsey's
OL,12,Fpoliticians take action to ensure
OL,13,Fislanders have a good standard of
OL,14,Fliving through access to housing,
OL,15,Fhealthy food and areas to exercise.
OL,17,FDr Brink adds: "I think we need to
OL,18,Fchange the narrative from bad health
OL,19,Fbeing a burden to good health being an
OL,20,Feconomic enabler.
